            "stanza_text": "Au matin, Elle entra chez Guy,\nPâle, ayant pourtant l'air d'être aise,\nBelle, avec un air alangui,\nDans sa robe couleur de fraise."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Dans la maison, qui se soumit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Elle entra comme une voisine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et tout de suite, Elle se mit",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "A fourrager dans la cuisine.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans la maison, qui se soumit,\nElle entra comme une voisine,\nEt tout de suite, Elle se mit\nA fourrager dans la cuisine."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "O doux régal que parfois j'eus !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Avec de jolis airs tartuffes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Elle arrosa d'un très bon jus",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Des œufs du jour, brouillés aux truffes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "O doux régal que parfois j'eus !\nAvec de jolis airs tartuffes,\nElle arrosa d'un très bon jus\nDes œufs du jour, brouillés aux truffes,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Et les servit. Guy déjeuna,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Trouvant le destin peu sévère.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi qu'aux noces de Cana,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Un vin rose empourprait son verre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et les servit. Guy déjeuna,\nTrouvant le destin peu sévère.\nAinsi qu'aux noces de Cana,\nUn vin rose empourprait son verre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Puis, tandis qu'il en savourait",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'aux dernières gouttelettes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Qu'un rayon de soleil dorait,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Elle servit les côtelettes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Puis, tandis qu'il en savourait\nJusqu'aux dernières gouttelettes\nQu'un rayon de soleil dorait,\nElle servit les côtelettes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ayant sur ce point triomphé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Sans chiffonner sa collerette,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Tandis que Guy prit son café",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "En fumant une cigarette,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ayant sur ce point triomphé\nSans chiffonner sa collerette,\nTandis que Guy prit son café\nEn fumant une cigarette,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Pour achever l'enchantement,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Elle prit un bel exemplaire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Du livre, et lut très lentement",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Quelques strophes de Baudelaire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour achever l'enchantement,\nElle prit un bel exemplaire\nDu livre, et lut très lentement\nQuelques strophes de Baudelaire."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Puis elle joua du Wagner",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Au piano, montrant le lobe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "D'une oreille rose, et dans l'air",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Volaient les parfums de sa robe.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Puis elle joua du Wagner\nAu piano, montrant le lobe\nD'une oreille rose, et dans l'air\nVolaient les parfums de sa robe."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Elle s'agenouilla. Ses yeux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Disaient toutes sortes de choses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Et Guy, se roulant dans les cieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Baisa longtemps ses lèvres roses.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle s'agenouilla. Ses yeux\nDisaient toutes sortes de choses,\nEt Guy, se roulant dans les cieux,\nBaisa longtemps ses lèvres roses."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Et dans son bonheur affermi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Comme un roi jeune et plein de gloire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Il égarait ses doigts parmi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "La grande chevelure noire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et dans son bonheur affermi\nComme un roi jeune et plein de gloire,\nIl égarait ses doigts parmi\nLa grande chevelure noire."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Il planait, comme un Séraphin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Dans le ciel où tout est dictame ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Puis il dit, s'éveillant enfin :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Mais qui donc êtes-vous, madame ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il planait, comme un Séraphin,\nDans le ciel où tout est dictame ;\nPuis il dit, s'éveillant enfin :\nMais qui donc êtes-vous, madame ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Moi ? dit-elle, s'il vous souvient",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "De votre désir, je suis celle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Que l'on attendait, et qui vient,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Et dont l'œil d'or sombre étincelle.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moi ? dit-elle, s'il vous souvient\nDe votre désir, je suis celle\nQue l'on attendait, et qui vient,\nEt dont l'œil d'or sombre étincelle."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "En ceci, rien d'original.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Tout est simple, dans cette affaire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "J'ai lu l'annonce du journal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et je suis la bonne à tout faire !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "En ceci, rien d'original.\nTout est simple, dans cette affaire.\nJ'ai lu l'annonce du journal,\nEt je suis la bonne à tout faire !"
        }
